        {
            "id": 0,
            "start": 0.0,
            "end": 1.62,
            "original_text": "А у вас теж так само.",
            "translated_text": "And it's the same with you.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_00",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_0.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "start": 2.54,
            "end": 11.46,
            "original_text": "Від себе ховаєшся, дні проковтуєш, виклики оминаєш, змін боїшся, звуки тримтиш.",
            "translated_text": "You hide from yourself, you swallow days, you avoid challenges, you are afraid of changes, you suppress sounds.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_00",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_1.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "start": 12.18,
            "end": 13.06,
            "original_text": "Спробуй інакше.",
            "translated_text": "Try another way.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_2.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "start": 14.1,
            "end": 24.24,
            "original_text": "Рано чекаєш, нове любиш, чуже приймаєш, лице під вітер, майбутнє мрієш, плани штовхаєш.",
            "translated_text": "You wait early, you love new things, you accept others, you face the wind, you dream of the future, you push your plans.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_3.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "start": 24.24,
            "end": 27.54,
            "original_text": "Дні такі сірі, але ж фарби в тебе.",
            "translated_text": "The days are so gray, but you have scars.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_4.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "start": 27.54,
            "end": 32.62,
            "original_text": "Чекати так важко, але ти зможеш, і буває страшно.",
            "translated_text": "It's so hard to wait, but you can, and it's scary.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_5.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "start": 33.16,
            "end": 38.42,
            "original_text": "Але злість сильніша, час минає, а попереду більше.",
            "translated_text": "But anger is stronger, time is passing, and more is ahead.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_6.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "start": 39.06,
            "end": 42.08,
            "original_text": "Яке ж завтра буде, все буде добре.",
            "translated_text": "Whatever tomorrow will be, everything will be fine.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_7.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "start": 42.66,
            "end": 44.86,
            "original_text": "Школа англійської Грін Форест.",
            "translated_text": "Green Forest School of English.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_8.wav",
            "status": "rendered"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "start": 45.52,
            "end": 49.78,
            "original_text": "У нас так багато страхів, але мрій більше.",
            "translated_text": "We have so many fears, but more dreams.",
            "speaker_id": "SPEAKER_01",
            "gender": "Female",
            "voice_id": null,
            "audio_path": "projects\\cache_audio\\seg_9.wav",
